Catastrophic Forgetting Check Visualization. Before/After benchmark comparison. X-axis: Tasks (Capital of France, 25*4+100, Explain RAG, MMLU sample, HumanEval). Y-axis: Accuracy (0-100%). Two grouped bars per task: Baseline (blue) vs Fine-tuned (orange). Threshold line at -5% drift. Warning zone shaded red below -10%. Annotation: "OK: <5% drift", "Warning: 5-10%", "Critical: >10%". German labels.